Text: EMCA RE Distemper some infoThanks for the additional information thats way more succinct and clear than anything I found Im not sure TWRC will test for which kind of distemper it is if the treatment is the same Theyre an underfunded nonprofit is there any other kind and I doubt theyll worrry about identifying the exact bug involved I think maybe if your dogs distemper shots are up to date youre ok A roommates cat caught FIV from a hostile stray on Fargo unfortunately I think we have to assume unknown critters could be a threat to household pets I do foster strays sometimes but I dont let them near my own cats until I get clearance from my vet From Wild Kingdom on the Bayou Carla Yahoo Groups Sponsor Get your FREE credit report with a FREE CreditCheck Monitoring Service trial ACHqaBbQCAAySSFAANoOolBTM To unsubscribe from this group send an email to Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms
